<h1 id="welcome-banner" class="text-center">Welcome to Quest Builder, a web application that puts you right in the middle of the story. You will make crucial decisions each step along the way that effect the way the story unfolds and ultimately determines whether or not you complete your quest! Here is how to get started:</h1>

<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
  <div class="callout">
    <h3 class="text-center panel-header"><strong>Sign Up or Sign In</strong><h3>
    <p>
      Sign Up or Sign In so you can save your progress as your quest unfolds.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
  <div class="callout">
    <h3 class="text-center panel-header"><strong><%= link_to 'Create A Character', new_user_character_path(current_user) %></strong><h3>
    <p>
      Using our custom character creation form, create your character that will embark upon one or many epic quests. You are able to customize such attributes as physical traits...
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
  <div class="callout">
    <h3 class="text-center panel-header"><strong>Begin Your Quest</strong><h3>
    <p>
      Select one of our quests and start questing! Your progress will be saved so you can sign out and then later resume your quest right where you left off. Good luck!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
